ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]

WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([p].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Comments] AS [c0]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([c0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([p].[Id] = [c0].[PostId])) DESC, [p].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id]

    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Content], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[PostId]

WHERE ([a].[IsAbandoned] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([a].[NextTryTime] <= @__Now_0)
ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]
